{"tid":1720495,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[溫故知新 + 經驗整合] 全民繼續升級：心態、裝備、技巧、戰術","createTime":"2019-11-14T11:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T11:51:43.000Z","uid":179379,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2cec6006870c76c477348f593f7acaa7f817a423","tid":1720495,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:15:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. 必須保持警戒</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n包括勇武、和理非、街坊<br />\n要知道武裝曱甴係極度仇視香港人<br />\n中環已經有個西裝友被打到入icu<br />\n只要你唔小心，就好容易被咬，甚至被殺<br />\n<br />\n出到嚟唔係玩，唔係吹水，唔係嘉年華<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">請認真看待，每個人搵返個適合你嘅角色</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. 唔好落單 + 換衫</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n噚晚我哋荃灣已經失去咗一個手足<br />\n今朝上水又有女仔差啲被綁架<br />\n<br />\n所以當你<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">落單</span>時<br />\n必須<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">換衫變返普通路人</span><br />\n<br />\n仲要時刻留意<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">有冇人跟蹤自己</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1171401/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1171401/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. 前線裝備</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n噚晚天水圍小朋友被催淚彈射頭仲昏迷𡁵<br />\n浸大記者被射中眼<br />\n所以裝備好重要<br />\n記住，依家班曱甴係每次都水平開槍<br />\n<br />\n如果要同綠曱甴正面對抗<br />\n必須戴<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">頭盔</span>﹐最起碼都要有頂bump cap<br />\n最好有<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">防彈眼罩+其他防具</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1335747/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1335747/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">4. 隱藏身份</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n魔法師、裝修師傅、神獸召喚師、魔法調製師<br />\n以及其他高危職業<br />\n必須根據我之前個post講點包好個樣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1583191/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1583191/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">唔好以為校園範圍安全就除罩</span><br />\n一樣大把紅媒、外人、CCTV<br />\n<br />\n而<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">隱藏身份唔等於一定係blackbloc</span><br />\n例如哨兵就必須咩都唔包，化身成普通路人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">5. 哨兵</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n哨兵係好重要<br />\n只要你哨得好，就可以<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">避免手足被包圍</span><br />\n<br />\n但正確嘅資訊傳達亦都好重要<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">一句過，圖 + 時間 + 確實地點 / 方向 + 種類 + 數量 + 行動</span><br />\n<br />\n如果大家都做到<br />\nadmin就可以減少閱讀同整理時間<br />\n隨時出多一兩個post救人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">6. 現場資訊傳達</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n現場必須搵人<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">睇哨兵channel同地圖</span><br />\n依家睇慢幾分鐘都隨時走唔切<br />\n<br />\n和理非 / 街坊可以幫手做呢個角色<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">有資訊要大聲同現場手足講</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">7. 現場需要Tutor</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n因為好多新手加入<br />\n但佢哋一嚟面對嘅唔係新手村，而係boss<br />\n<br />\n所以請現場有經驗嘅手足幫手<br />\n如果見到有唔對路、有人企得太前、留得太耐、有被包圍風險、有人企喺度唔知做咩<br />\n都必須要<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">提醒其他人</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">8. 行動目的</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔同地方有唔同打法<br />\n大學必須要守<br />\n黎明行動阻返工令經濟受影響<br />\n公路隧道用嚟塞交通<br />\n商業區打經濟令舖頭閂門<br />\n仲有裝修神獸快閃<br />\n<br />\n所以除非必須死守嘅地方<br />\n其他<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">達到目的就可以離開 / 轉場</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">9. 大學手足</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大校手足必須諗吓未來方向<br />\n大學係好好嘅基地去儲物資同兵<br />\n但儲完一定要諗點用<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">當你冇事嘅時候就要諗點支援其他地方</span><br />\n<br />\n例如今日暴大好多人但全日淨守<br />\n但紅土已經打到仆晒街<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n希望暴大唔會再出現炒車、炸電箱、爆玻璃等戇鳩行為<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">10. 足夠休息</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n狗有輪班<br />\n所以手足都唔可以日日頂足咁多個鐘<br />\n一定要<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">分配好休息時間</span><br />\n<br />\n唔夠瞓<br />\n除咗影響體力之外<br />\n仲會影響判斷力"},{"pid":"27599db2a0cc8d47fe28de949bb0dfeb0c96fbc5","tid":1720495,"uid":172893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:18:14.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"2ee02fab6b43f9c07cb5bb3126cdf16202569ad2","tid":1720495,"uid":30246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:20:25.000Z","msg":"推上熱門<br />\n好有用"},{"pid":"ccf612aec69397084979464eb6d6115b54e2db25","tid":1720495,"uid":30246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:20:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d859323653813a5c3f704aab41a2cbb045a94d5f","tid":1720495,"uid":30246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:20:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fa1f400b4cade324ccd0556ca00c7c6fd54e6619","tid":1720495,"uid":30246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:21:10.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推"},{"pid":"2a52b494ed1ce114a91d5e5d3cc29accb186b2f8","tid":1720495,"uid":30246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:22:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fbc420277530142841fb2aaa3a2707619b38d352","tid":1720495,"uid":30246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:23:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cbccdc148d955f60eb5ba38098474df2c9428e96","tid":1720495,"uid":54084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:25:46.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"2e00fc4e7944943908ecde9a1d0da8b43d722e76","tid":1720495,"uid":30246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:31:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"294f21879f84598861a83c657bdece6413aae6a6","tid":1720495,"uid":140893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:32:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38a864ab5e02aa905708b831c4fd5366d5ad42da","tid":1720495,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd254536c3f9a19f2b64d28f053e83824df564ee","tid":1720495,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d14106ffadde5430e5bafb0927ef0c8e0c7ee5","tid":1720495,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:30:35.000Z","msg":"果然標題唔夠爆<br />\n係冇連登仔睇"},{"pid":"dc42fa4fdba6dd8adba86d0ab697276d5c97ee99","tid":1720495,"uid":247064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:13:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d0ffe8ef8799f878744689029a8699aa9a46093","tid":1720495,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T07:13:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">11.18黎明行動文宣不足啊<br />\n幫手推到文宣組見到</span>"},{"pid":"67ab3fb194d6f7d201446ec995fcdc933b75cab1","tid":1720495,"uid":245305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:17:07.000Z","msg":"推 全民武裝打狗"},{"pid":"b8bc647a0cc1a78dbe227a9e3590bb14ecac07ff","tid":1720495,"uid":60477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:29:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"34e1ebed4efeadab6c6eaa5adaa278cf6fb1843c","tid":1720495,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:30:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d442940c3553f2ddecdad523c4da28a976884df2","tid":1720495,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:34:52.000Z","msg":"推，真有用"},{"pid":"6ae3cee74a929caf0ebb7ba2d4051a1b2bced055","tid":1720495,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:35:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">1118 再會黎明</div></strong>"},{"pid":"f661f77dc36a54dc1e0fd62b8cf1321593b44c56","tid":1720495,"uid":98479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:39:33.000Z","msg":"實用post"},{"pid":"c609684da676958f0221893aee31bdb373967b55","tid":1720495,"uid":294331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:51:43.000Z","msg":"講得好岩"}]}